snippet.description:
This was my first visit to US-4064, Lake Ramsey Savannah WMA.  It's a beautiful Longleaf Pine Savannah near Covington, LA.  I set up on the tailgate and deployed my SS-25 tuned for 10m.  I could never have anticipated the DX I'd get that day.  Italy and Guatemala on 10m and several other countries on 15m. It was fantastic.  As N0RCP said, POTA is Fun  You got that right, Ray.
Come along for a fun activation with laughs and a whole lot of DX.
#pota 
#hamradio 
#radioantenna 
#hamradioantenna 
#parksontheair 
#radiocommunication 

Equipment used;

 @YaesuUSAOfficial  FT-891
 @ecoworthy_official  20ah battery
 @ABRindCoax  
 @ChameleonAntennaOfficial  SS-25
 @GigaPartsHuntsville  
 @DXEngineering  
 @ParksOnTheAir 
https://www.simo.co/products/solis-lite-hotspot
 @DJI  Osmo Pocket 3
 @wrcoils  
 @smartlogger  for logging.  


Thanks for watching.  Please comment, Like, and Share.  Also, please subscribe if you find the channel helpful and/or fun.
73
Paul
KJ5GKK

